<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lecture-v">lecture <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lektʃə(r)/    美 /'lektʃər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>讲课；作讲座；演讲：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>lectures on</strong> literature at Manchester University.
他在曼彻斯特大学教文学。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>教训；训斥：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He's always <strong>lecturing</strong> me <strong>about</strong> the way I dress.
他总是对我的穿着说三道四。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>lecturer /'lektʃərə(r)/ n [C]   </p></div>